          <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated based on several resellers (available here: https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Sodium-Sulphite-92-96-97-Na2SO3_1600425774843.html?spm=a2700.galleryofferlist.normal_offer.d_title.34227a03w3Sk27&amp;s=p, https://fengdachem.en.made-in-china.com/product/tZMAyhCrZRYk/China-Sodium-Sulphite-Fengda-90-92-Min-Food-Grade-Price-Na2so3-7757-83-7-Sodium-Sulphite-Sodium-Sulfite.html, https://www.indiamart.com/proddetail/sodium-sulphite-15042862788.html, https://www.indiamart.com/proddetail/sodium-sulphite-food-grade-23438412930.html, all last accessed 2022-07-25).
The price was converted to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.USD.EUR.SP00.A, last accessed on 2022-02-15) and adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://appsso.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/nui/show.do?dataset=sts_inpp_a&amp;lang=en, last accessed on 2022-05-04).</comment>
